BUILDING EvilPoison
===================

Using GNU make to build
-----------------------

1) Edit settings.make to suit what you want.  Instructions are included by any
   user-editable option.

2) Run 'make'

3) Run 'make install'

That's it.  The README file has information on starting evilpoison.

Using CMake to build
--------------------

1) Run 'cmake .'

2) Run 'make -f Makefile'

3) Run 'make -f Makefile install' (this is not yet implemented)
